捐赠物资“直达”武汉目标医院的另类样本：百万粉丝博主倒逼物流改变收件目的地。
Donations "direct" to Wuhan target hospital of alternative samples: millions of fans bloggers forced logistics to change the destination.
洪小棠2020-02-01 23:21。
Begonia 2020-02-01 23: 21.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 洪小棠随着疫情防控工作的持续开展，医疗物资紧缺一直伴随着一线医护人员的救治工作，一面是社会各界捐赠的物资源源不断的涌入武汉，另一面是武汉的发热患者定点医院却依旧向社会发出求援消息，引起舆论关注。
With the continuous development of disease prevention and control, the shortage of medical supplies has been accompanied by the first-line medical personnel, on the one hand, donated materials from all sectors of society poured into Wuhan, on the other hand, Wuhan fever patients designated hospitals are still sent to the community to call for help, aroused public concern.
。
.
经济观察网此前报道，社会捐赠的医疗物资统一配送至当地红十字会，此后再统一调配发放，但物资能否及时送到至医院依然是个问题。
The network had previously reported that donations of medical supplies had been distributed centrally to the local Red Cross and then consolidated for distribution, but timely delivery to hospitals remained a problem.
。
.
作为一个普通的捐赠者，如何将自己定向捐献的抗疫物资直接送达指定医院？。
As an ordinary donor, how can I deliver my targeted donation of anti-epidemic materials directly to the designated hospital?
佩儿的哥哥也是武汉某医院的一名一线医生，疫情发生以来一直在一线救治患者，听说哥哥所在地区医疗物资十分紧张，佩儿心急如焚，哪里有第一手医疗物资她就赶紧联系掏钱买下来，佩儿告诉记者目前她已经把价值40多万的物资发出去了。
Her brother, a first-line doctor at a Wuhan hospital, has been treating patients first-line since the outbreak, hearing that her brother's area was strained and Pele was desperate to buy medical supplies first-hand. She told reporters she had sent more than 400,000 items.
。
.
然而，佩儿指定捐赠给协和医院的医疗物资配送并不顺利，物资没有达到指定医院，而是配送到了红十字会的仓库。
However, the distribution of medical supplies earmarked by Peel for Concorde Hospital did not proceed smoothly, and supplies did not reach the designated hospital, but were distributed to the Red Cross warehouse.
。
.
记者从物流方面确认，医疗物资通过邮政、顺丰等物流运输时，如果选择红十字会通道或者绿色通道，即便填写的收件地址为定向捐赠的某家医院，物流配送时还是会送到武汉市红十字会的仓库--武汉国际博览中心。
Reporters confirmed from logistics, such as medical supplies through the postal, Shunfeng and other logistics, if the Red Cross channel or green channel, even if filled in the address of a targeted donation of a hospital, logistics and distribution will be sent to Wuhan City Red Cross warehouse - Wuhan International Expo Center.
。
.
佩儿对上述物资运输流程规定有些质疑。
Peel has some doubts about the procedures for the shipment of these goods.
“现在是医疗物资非常缺乏的时候，肯定希望物资能够第一时间送到医生手里，快递单上填写的地址明明是武汉协和医院，但物流还是交给了国博中心。
"Now is the time of great shortage of medical supplies, certainly hope that supplies can be delivered to the first time to the doctor, express delivery list clearly written address is Wuhan Concorde Hospital, but the logistics was handed over to the National Expo Center.
为什么不经过我同意就直接送到那里了？”佩儿说。
Why did you send it there without my permission? "said Pearl."
。
.
记者随即拨通邮政物流快递员的电话，快递员称，“医疗物资我们规定必须先送到红十字会。
Reporters dialed the courier service, the courier said. "We require medical supplies to be delivered to the Red Cross first.
无论个人捐赠者将快递的收件地址填到哪里，都将由红十字会接收入库并统一调配。
Wherever an individual donor fills in the courier address, the Red Cross receives and consolidates them.
“。
"
这也意味着，在当前机制下，即便是寄往指定的武汉当地医院，也仍然要再红十字会的仓库“过手”。
This also means that under the current mechanism, even to designated local hospitals in Wuhan, the Red Cross warehouse will still have to "pass through."
。
.
佩儿对记者表示，“如果物资先送给红十字会，那至于分配得到你想要捐赠的医院，什么时候分配到，这个时效期肯定会慢，现在医疗物资又这么紧缺……”。
"If the supplies are given to the Red Cross first, when will the distribution be slow and medical supplies are so scarce..." she told reporters.
1月31日这一天，佩儿为了捐赠物资与物流公司多次交涉，然而第一批捐赠的物资已经被红十字会签收了。
On January 31, Peel made several representations to the logistics company for donations of supplies, but the first batch was signed by the Red Cross.
。
.
佩儿仍然想让自己捐赠的物资尽快送到医院并选择继续跟物流沟通，要求更改快递接收地点。
Pearl still wanted her donations to be delivered to the hospital as soon as possible and chose to continue to communicate with the logistics to request a change in the express delivery location.
与此同时，微博上有着130多万粉丝的她发布了该物流事件的一条状态，并引发了众多关注。
Meanwhile, with more than 1.3 million followers on Weibo, she released a status report on the logistics event, which drew a lot of attention.
。
.
佩儿对记者表示，“2月1日早上快递打来电话，一共三件货，一件已经被红十字会签收了，还有两个在路上，他们希望我能够把微博删除，然后他们保证我的这些物资能送到医院，已经签收的也帮我追回并发给协和医院。
"On the morning of Feb. 1, three items arrived by express, one was signed by the Red Cross and two were on the way," Peel told reporters. "They wanted me to delete the microblog, and then they promised that my supplies would be delivered to the hospital and those that had been signed would be recovered and sent to Concorde Hospital.
”。
"
2月1日下午，佩儿告诉记者，快递已经专门将这三件货单独取出来，送到了协和医院。
On the afternoon of Feb. 1, Pei told reporters that express had taken the three pieces out separately and sent them to Concorde Hospital.
这一案例或许说明，配送体系并非没有能力帮助抗疫物资直达医院。
This case may suggest that the distribution system is not incapable of helping the disease to reach the hospital directly.
。
.
佩儿能够将捐赠的医疗物资直送到指定医院或许因其拥有着百万粉丝的自媒体平台影响力，但更多捐赠者并没有这一优势，他们正等待着红十字会将自己捐赠的物资发给需要的医院。
Pele may be able to send donated medical supplies directly to designated hospitals because of its impact on a self-media platform with millions of fans, but many more donors do not have the advantage and are waiting for the Red Cross to distribute its donations to needy hospitals.
。
.
根据1月31日湖北省新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作第十场新闻发布会的说法，目前武汉接收捐赠主要有两种方式，一是定向捐赠，需签署三方定向捐赠协议，落实到授权主体。
According to the press conference of January 31, 2007, the 10th press conference on the prevention and control of the new coronavirus infection in Hubei Province, Wuhan has two main ways to receive donations.
二是非定向捐赠，所捐赠物资将拨付到市防控指挥部，统一调配使用。
Second, non-targeted donations, donated materials will be allocated to the Municipal Command of Control, unified deployment and use.
。
.
而就在佩儿的物资到达医生手中的当天即2月1日，武汉市人民政府官网又发布了《武汉市红十字会感谢各界爱心答复各方疑问》中表示，为进一步缩短捐赠物资的运转时间，武汉市红十字会对定向捐赠流程作出了适当调整，境内外单位或个人如有定向捐赠医院，可直接与定向捐赠医疗机构对接，确认后可直接将物资发往受捐单位。
The Red Cross Society of Wuhan City has made appropriate adjustments to the targeted donation process to further shorten the operation time of the donated materials. Units or individuals inside or outside the country who have a targeted donation hospital may dock directly with the designated donation facility, confirming that the materials can be sent directly to the recipient unit.
。
.
